hat corresponds to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol. When an annotation’s","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"role":"symbol"}}}